DATA & PRIVACY DISCLAIMER

This is a completely offline, self-hosted tool. All data you enter into the
Software is stored locally on your own machine in plain JSON files.

THE AUTHORS AND CONTRIBUTORS OF THIS SOFTWARE PROVIDE NO GUARANTEE, WARRANTY,
OR ASSURANCE REGARDING:

  • The security or protection of any third-party data stored or processed
    through this Software.
  • Protection against unauthorized access, data loss, or data corruption.
  • Compliance with any data protection regulations (including but not limited
    to GDPR, CCPA, or similar laws).

It is the sole responsibility of the user to ensure that sensitive data is
handled appropriately, backed up securely, and used in accordance with
applicable laws and regulations.

